pr_body:
PR for issue #325

Added support for timezone param in api_occurrences() function to make possible api calls with timezone param, for example:
```
$('#calendar').fullCalendar({
    events: '/schedule/api/occurrences?calendar_slug=test&timezone=America/Chicago'
});

```
Param timezone are described in https://fullcalendar.io/docs/timezone/timezone/

- Fixed the multi-GPU context where the test now utilizes a user-defined number of GPUs

For more information, see this [issue](https://github.com/awslabs/keras-apache-mxnet/issues/67)

@sandeep-krishnamurthy @roywei
